title: How to Make THE BEST Chicken Manchurian | From Everyday Ingredients | Indian-Chinese Cooking
description:
Chicken Manchurian is one of the most popular Chinese dishes in India. Often also made with cauliflower (Gobi Manchurian) or paneer (Paneer Manchurian), it's a slightly sweet, sour and savoury restaurant staple. No special ingredients required!

Here's the full recipe: http://adamliaw.com/recipe/chicken-manchurian/
